{"thag16.4:0.1":"Theragatha 16.4 ","thag16.4:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.4:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.4:0.4":"Ratthapalattheragatha ","thag16.4:1.1":"“Passa cittakatam bimbam, ","thag16.4:1.2":"arukayam samussitam; ","thag16.4:1.3":"Aturam bahusankappam, ","thag16.4:1.4":"yassa natthi dhuvam thiti. ","thag16.4:2.1":"Passa cittakatam rupam, ","thag16.4:2.2":"manina kundalena ca; ","thag16.4:2.3":"Atthim tacena onaddham, ","thag16.4:2.4":"saha vatthehi sobhati. ","thag16.4:3.1":"Alattakakata pada, ","thag16.4:3.2":"mukham cunnakamakkhitam; ","thag16.4:3.3":"Alam balassa mohaya, ","thag16.4:3.4":"no ca paragavesino. ","thag16.4:4.1":"Atthapadakata kesa, ","thag16.4:4.2":"netta anjanamakkhita; ","thag16.4:4.3":"Alam balassa mohaya, ","thag16.4:4.4":"no ca paragavesino. ","thag16.4:5.1":"Anjaniva nava citta, ","thag16.4:5.2":"putikayo alankato; ","thag16.4:5.3":"Alam balassa mohaya, ","thag16.4:5.4":"no ca paragavesino. ","thag16.4:6.1":"Odahi migavo pasam, ","thag16.4:6.2":"nasada vaguram migo; ","thag16.4:6.3":"Bhutva nivapam gacchama, ","thag16.4:6.4":"kandante migabandhake. ","thag16.4:7.1":"Chinno paso migavassa, ","thag16.4:7.2":"nasada vaguram migo; ","thag16.4:7.3":"Bhutva nivapam gacchama, ","thag16.4:7.4":"socante migaluddake. ","thag16.4:8.1":"Passami loke sadhane manusse, ","thag16.4:8.2":"Laddhana vittam na dadanti moha; ","thag16.4:8.3":"Luddha dhanam sannicayam karonti, ","thag16.4:8.4":"Bhiyyova kame abhipatthayanti. ","thag16.4:9.1":"Raja pasayhappathavim vijetva, ","thag16.4:9.2":"Sasagarantam mahimavasanto; ","thag16.4:9.3":"Oram samuddassa atittarupo, ","thag16.4:9.4":"Param samuddassapi patthayetha. ","thag16.4:10.1":"Raja ca anne ca bahu manussa, ","thag16.4:10.2":"Avitatanha maranam upenti; ","thag16.4:10.3":"Unava hutvana jahanti deham, ","thag16.4:10.4":"Kamehi lokamhi na hatthi titti. ","thag16.4:11.1":"Kandanti nam nati pakiriya kese, ","thag16.4:11.2":"Aho vata no amarati cahu; ","thag16.4:11.3":"Vatthena nam parutam niharitva, ","thag16.4:11.4":"Citam samodhaya tato dahanti. ","thag16.4:12.1":"So dayhati sulehi tujjamano, ","thag16.4:12.2":"Ekena vatthena pahaya bhoge; ","thag16.4:12.3":"Na miyamanassa bhavanti tana, ","thag16.4:12.4":"Nati ca mitta atha va sahaya. ","thag16.4:13.1":"Dayadaka tassa dhanam haranti, ","thag16.4:13.2":"Satto pana gacchati yena kammam; ","thag16.4:13.3":"Na miyamanam dhanamanveti kinci, ","thag16.4:13.4":"Putta ca dara ca dhananca rattham. ","thag16.4:14.1":"Na dighamayum labhate dhanena, ","thag16.4:14.2":"Na capi vittena jaram vihanti; ","thag16.4:14.3":"Appam hidam jivitamahu dhira, ","thag16.4:14.4":"Asassatam vipparinamadhammam. ","thag16.4:15.1":"Addha dalidda ca phusanti phassam, ","thag16.4:15.2":"Balo ca dhiro ca tatheva phuttho; ","thag16.4:15.3":"Balo hi balya vadhitova seti, ","thag16.4:15.4":"Dhiro ca no vedhati phassaphuttho. ","thag16.4:16.1":"Tasma hi pannava dhanena seyya, ","thag16.4:16.2":"Yaya vosanamidhadhigacchati; ","thag16.4:16.3":"Abyositatta hi bhavabhavesu, ","thag16.4:16.4":"Papani kammani karoti moha. ","thag16.4:17.1":"Upeti gabbhanca paranca lokam, ","thag16.4:17.2":"Samsaramapajja paramparaya; ","thag16.4:17.3":"Tassappapanno abhisaddahanto, ","thag16.4:17.4":"Upeti gabbhanca paranca lokam. ","thag16.4:18.1":"Coro yatha sandhimukhe gahito, ","thag16.4:18.2":"Sakammuna hannati papadhammo; ","thag16.4:18.3":"Evam paja pecca paramhi loke, ","thag16.4:18.4":"Sakammuna hannati papadhammo. ","thag16.4:19.1":"Kama hi citra madhura manorama, ","thag16.4:19.2":"Viruparupena mathenti cittam; ","thag16.4:19.3":"Adinavam kamagunesu disva, ","thag16.4:19.4":"Tasma aham pabbajitomhi raja. ","thag16.4:20.1":"Dumapphalaniva patanti manava, ","thag16.4:20.2":"Dahara ca vuddha ca sarirabheda; ","thag16.4:20.3":"Etampi disva pabbajitomhi raja, ","thag16.4:20.4":"Apannakam samannameva seyyo. ","thag16.4:21.1":"Saddhayaham pabbajito, ","thag16.4:21.2":"upeto jinasasane; ","thag16.4:21.3":"Avanjha mayham pabbajja, ","thag16.4:21.4":"anano bhunjami bhojanam. ","thag16.4:22.1":"Kame adittato disva, ","thag16.4:22.2":"Jatarupani satthato; ","thag16.4:22.3":"Gabbhavokkantito dukkham, ","thag16.4:22.4":"Nirayesu mahabbhayam. ","thag16.4:23.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","thag16.4:23.2":"samvegam alabhim tada; ","thag16.4:23.3":"Soham viddho tada santo, ","thag16.4:23.4":"sampatto asavakkhayam. ","thag16.4:24.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag16.4:24.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thag16.4:24.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thag16.4:24.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thag16.4:25.1":"Yassatthaya pabbajito, ","thag16.4:25.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag16.4:25.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thag16.4:25.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo”ti. ","thag16.4:25.5":"… Ratthapalo thero …. "}